# Main branch workflow

- Always do all work on `main` in this repository.
- Never create, switch to, or commit on feature/topic branches unless the user explicitly overrides this rule.
- At the start of each new session, before any code changes:
  - run `git checkout main`
  - run `git pull --ff-only origin main`
- Before committing or pushing, verify the current branch is still `main`.
